  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreText\/CTCharacterCollection\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:35:13Z\n---\n\n# CTCharacterCollection\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nConstants that specify character collections.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum CTCharacterCollection\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CTCharacterCollection.identityMapping**: The character identifier is equal to the glyph index.\n- **CTCharacterCollection.adobeCNS1**: The Adobe-CNS1 mapping.\n- **CTCharacterCollection.adobeGB1**: The Adobe-GB1 mapping.\n- **CTCharacterCollection.adobeJapan1**: The Adobe-Japan1 mapping.\n- **CTCharacterCollection.adobeJapan2**: The Adobe-Japan2 mapping.\n- **CTCharacterCollection.adobeKorea1**: The Adobe-Korea1 mapping.\n\n## Deprecated\n\n- **kCTIdentityMappingCharacterCollection**: The character identifier is equal to the glyph index.\n- **kCTAdobeCNS1CharacterCollection**: The Adobe-CNS1 mapping.\n- **kCTAdobeGB1CharacterCollection**: The Adobe-GB1 mapping.\n- **kCTAdobeJapan1CharacterCollection**: The Adobe-Japan1 mapping.\n- **kCTAdobeJapan2CharacterCollection**: The Adobe-Japan2 mapping.\n- **kCTAdobeKorea1CharacterCollection**: The Adobe-Korea1 mapping.\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
